             were indicted for <rs id="t18331017-3-off12" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18331017-3-off12" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18331017-3-off12" type="offenceSubcategory" value="housebreaking"></interp>
               feloniously breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18331017-3-victim122" type="victimName">
                           David 
                           Jones
                        <interp inst="t18331017-3-victim122" type="surname" value="Jones"></interp>
